{"tid":255224,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（深夜舒情）覺唔覺人愈大愈難開心","createTime":"2017-05-23T18:11:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T18:20:46.000Z","uid":63219,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"941ed1a71a5bf85670dee30ce6ad30cb489eff72","tid":255224,"uid":63219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:11:08.000Z","msg":"話說小弟今日岩岩追完射雕英雄傳<br />\n唔係講笑真係好正豆 <br />\n佢拍出黎既背景好易明但好深奧<br />\n成套劇有好多大自然既野<br />\n配埋果兩首普通話歌<br />\n唔係講笑 我真係想生活係果個時代<br />\n一切一切都係好簡單 好寫意<br />\n反而時代愈進步愈冇初初既幸福哩下真<br />\n果陣小小事已經好開心<br />\n可能有人覺得拍戲姐 點會真<br />\n但我就唔係咁睇<br />\n睇完套劇好空虛啊 仲有冇其他好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e607aa0023f337482cd10854c4cdb3b0f515be","tid":255224,"uid":63219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:12:03.000Z","msg":"其實都係夜媽媽先諗到哩啲野"},{"pid":"6ebc8b46bd7136d675daf8b5c0b144decbfd1e4c","tid":255224,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:12:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/24/021202_cd8c14af87b471f363663b3d9bc636dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F24%2F021202_cd8c14af87b471f363663b3d9bc636dd.jpg&h=dc419c84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b58b54725175c3c1966d7b1aef412f0ea71df26f","tid":255224,"uid":63219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:14:30.000Z","msg":"每日都返學放學 返工放工 機械式生活<br />\n突然覺得啲人環遊世界真係好型 小小錢咁去見識"},{"pid":"1d33edff399a871eba14e488f522437c0c14e1c6","tid":255224,"uid":91471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:20:46.000Z","msg":"以前番工都會覺得開心<br />\n而家慢慢睇清人心<br />\n覺得好恐怖好假<br />\n唔想再番<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}